rooms.roomDescription: Radiant hardwood floor.  Approx 11x19. Picturesque windows. Adjacent full bath access.  Closet offers family/playroom/home office storage or potential for first floor bdrm, if desired.
Wall to wall carpet.  Expansive 19x23  Multiple closets. Full bathroom.

Generous entertaining eat in kitchen.  Hardwood floor.  Gas stoves.  French doors to glass surround sunroom addition facing west to capture painted sunset skies, natural surround and seasonal mountain views.
Barn and shed on property. Barn approx 22x30 with cathedral height ceiling and cement floor.
Poured concrete foundation.  Main basement accessible from inside home and bilco doors.  Additional separate basement storage area with walk in/out access from outside.
Full bathroom separated between lavatory and shower.
Hardwood floor foyer opens to living room.  French doors to parlor.  Stairs to side.
Parlor room with wood burning fireplace.  Wall to wall carpet.  French doors to eat in kitchen.
Full hall bathroom currently used as half bath (noted as half bath on bathroom count) with laundry.
Expanded.  Gas burning fireplace.  Sliders to patio.  Hardwood floors.
Wall to wall carpet.  Dual primary potential between size and ensuite bathroom. 13.1' x 19/6'.  Wide entry pocket doors into bathroom. Gazing balcony.

data.description: Facing straight west and just off the eat in kitchen, the four season sunroom with heat/ac and adjacent deck with awning provide year round peaceful enjoyment of spectacular painted sky sunsets, seasonal mountain views and natural surround. The expansive living room with gas fireplace, cozy parlor room with wood burning fireplace and beaming sunroom showcasing the stunning natural surround all flow to and from the eat in kitchen. The east wing addition features radiant hardwood floor family room/office/playroom.  The generous closet and full bathroom present potential for first floor bedroom option.  Dual primary option also exists with generous en-suite upper level bedrooms. Residence approach greets with fenced raised garden bed and cement floor two bay approx. 22x30 barn.  Cleared trail on property opens to serene Little Wappinger Creek. Potential pool site(s). Tucked away between Rhinebeck and Millbrook yet convenient to both and the Taconic. Country exhale awaits!
